{"tid":603483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曾上游：擁5層樓靠投資，唔會上客人屋企","createTime":"2018-03-23T19:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T06:51:08.000Z","uid":178036,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ce1c3c25229942090f3ab0f4878d13e87ae32d","tid":603483,"uid":178036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T19:34:14.000Z","msg":"二十五歲的曾上游，是一名私影少女。她自稱，2016年護理學系畢業後，曾任職一年註冊護士，月薪三萬多元。但因為覺得這份工不適合自己，又想有更大發展空間，所以辭去護士工作，主力做私影妹。 <br />\n<br />\n她本月初接受傳媒訪問，說做私影和投資，而擁有五層在內地和澳門的物業。 有網民隨即上載懷疑她和客人不道德交易對話截圖，引起極大迴響。 <br />\n<br />\n其實在兩個月前，曾上游曾接受本刊訪問。對於自己做私影而擁有多層物業，她有自己的說法。 <br />\n<br />\n一五年時，她未大學畢業已買樓，「在香港很難申請到樓宇按揭，當時有一個朋友提醒我，其實可先在深圳置業，兩年後樓價升一倍，便有錢換香港樓，於是便到深圳買了人生第一層樓。」 <br />\n<br />\n當時的買入價是一百七十五萬(人民幣)。「首期加上雜費，約五十多萬。」 為何有錢付首期？「因為我在09年開始，已經是半工讀，讀中學時已做不同類型的兼職，以及當時很少花錢，所以儲了六、七年也儲到一些錢。」 <br />\n<br />\n之後為什麼有能力不斷置業？「因為我不止是儲錢，我都有作不同的投資，尤其是買樓，深圳的物業175萬買入，290多萬賣出，便賺了第一桶金，於是便可以買第二、第三層樓。」 <br />\n<br />\n私影的收入，足夠供樓和養家嗎？「是可以的，但前提是一定要很性感，影時裝一定不可以，市面上有很多這樣的模特兒，除非你是天姿國色。」 <br />\n<br />\n上周六，曾上游原本答允再受訪，回應不道德交易事件，但最後她以太忙為由而爽約。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_578197_0&amp;i=20180324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_578197_0%26i%3D20180324&d=cNPXH2SfTmEmQcKn40XQj54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9dad3232\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_578197_0%26i%3D20180324&h=ecb27e18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_578197_0&amp;i=20180324</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">未讀完大學就買到第一層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"9d00f9d32f5d88c88e614ac472e3857b5506f2c7","tid":603483,"uid":9863,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T19:45:09.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"ba3e6a76209cece807a7f3c72828280362abdd2c","tid":603483,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T19:47:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dcc40f8059c9d6c25cdb6e25e59397cb73752fe","tid":603483,"uid":12370,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T19:50:03.000Z","msg":"但係我到而家都唔明佢點解可以收咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9d629c70be55e31055bb75b6fe982a61043a98","tid":603483,"uid":75570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T20:03:37.000Z","msg":"是雞是公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f3d413c2ebc4efc7ad65e6d75742e430a5a0a1","tid":603483,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T21:57:55.000Z","msg":"毒撚好酸"},{"pid":"215337c2e5d72c62b8a30aee39e587281b920645","tid":603483,"uid":157138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:20:00.000Z","msg":"唔會上客人屋企 因為客人上你屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edfe5debeec6c94130daeb1cc2a698efaa43394","tid":603483,"uid":88252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:21:02.000Z","msg":"因為上酒店"},{"pid":"3a77708de383e5429e98eaaf3780c956a7b15601","tid":603483,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:23:34.000Z","msg":"出面已經有晒條平胸黑提多毛支那雞 d 相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇過，狗都唔屌"},{"pid":"bb788884742291279f70a743aeaece6f85c02381","tid":603483,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:25:45.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"09b2613184a32bfa3673ca116b2ce3ae684bb2ce","tid":603483,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:26:51.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"aad4162874538617e8ce0d5dd6f186f707ecfe4f","tid":603483,"uid":90609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T22:35:24.000Z","msg":"明明做雞..仲講到自己好叻咁..."},{"pid":"5368dbbc47535799789f41efc7f8a0fd9fbc1c2f","tid":603483,"uid":46245,"li